- Affordable

Faizan Movers offers reliable storage services for Dubai residents.

## 13. Move on Weekdays

Weekends in Dubai are crowded.
Choose Monday to Thursday for a smoother moving experience.

## 14. Don‚Äôt Lift Heavy Items Yourself

Back injuries are common during moving.
Let trained movers handle heavy items with the right tools like:

- Trolleys
- Sliders
- Straps
- Dollies

Your health comes first.

## 15. Check the New Home Before Moving In

Before moving, check:

- Water
- Electricity
- AC
- Door locks
- Lighting

Fixing things beforehand saves time and stress.

